B.a4d=new A.a1(B.Db,["Day Plan","Home","Log in","Sign up","Log out","My Plan","Admin","Announcements","Golden rules after surgery","Daily routine","Let's take this journey together, day by day \u2014 knowing what to eat and when.","This site is here to help and give you the plan that fits you. You're taking great steps \u2014 let's keep going.","Day","Before surgery","Goal","Sample day","Exercise","Drinks","Protein","Vegetables","Fruits","Carbs","Avoid","Full name","Email","Password","Gender","Male","Female","Height (cm)","Weight before (kg)","Latest weight (kg)","Surgery","Surgery date","Save","Complete your profile to see your plan","This week","Previous","Next","Photo \u2014 before","Photo \u2014 after","Continue","Uploading\u2026","Edit my info","Can I eat\u2026?","Type a food (e.g. chips, whey, dates)\u2026","Type any food and see if it fits your plan.","When","Allowed","With conditions","Better to avoid","Good for your plan","Not ideal for your plan","We don't have info on this yet. Please check with Dr Ahmed Abdel Salam's medical team.","Doctor view \u2014 Patients","Post an announcement","Publish","No patients yet","About the doctor","Dr. Ahmed Abd El Salam","Assistant Prof. of General & Laparoscopic Surgery, Kasr El-Ainy (Cairo University) \u2014 Bariatric Surgery Consultant",'One of Egypt\'s leading bariatric surgeons, member of IFSO and the Egyptian Society of Laparoscopic Surgery. Pioneer of the "Identical Sleeve" and Fast-Track Surgery techniques in the Middle East. He and his team support every patient at each step, before and after surgery.',"drahmedabdelsalam.com","This app supports \u2014 but does not replace \u2014 your surgeon's instructions. Always follow Dr. Ahmed Abdel Salam's team."],t.w)
